# Merglbot â€” Cursor ignore list (security + performance)
#
# Cursor blocks access to these files from Agent/Tab/Semantic search.
# This is best-effort protection; still follow MERGLBOT_AI_TOOLS.md and never paste secrets into prompts.
#
# Syntax: same as .gitignore
#
# Source: `merglbot-public/docs/templates/cursor/.cursorignore`
# GitHub: https://github.com/merglbot-public/docs/blob/main/templates/cursor/.cursorignore

# Secrets / env
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.env
**/*.env.*

# Agent local skills (if mistakenly created inside a repo/workspace)
**/.cursor/skills/**
**/.claude/skills/**

# Common credentials / keys
**/credentials.json
**/secrets.json
**/secrets/**
# Ignore common secret dump files, but do not hide source/docs with "secret" in the filename.
**/*secret*.env
**/*secret*.env.*
**/*secret*.json
**/*secret*.yml
**/*secret*.yaml
# Terraform vars often contain secrets
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/*.tfvars.*
**/*secret*.tfvars
**/*secret*.txt
**/*secret*.log
**/*secret*.csv
**/*secret*.toml
**/*secret*.ini
**/*secret*.properties
**/*.secret
**/*.secrets
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/id_rsa
**/id_dsa
**/id_ecdsa
**/id_ed25519
**/*service-account*.json
**/*sa-key*.json

# Package manager / CLI auth files
**/.npmrc
**/.pypirc
**/.netrc
**/.docker/config.json

# Cloud CLI creds (if copied into repo/workspace)
**/application_default_credentials.json
**/.aws/credentials
**/.aws/config
**/.config/gcloud/**

# Terraform sensitive inputs/state
**/*.tfvars
**/*.tfvars.json
**/*.tfvars.*
**/.terraform/**
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.*
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.backup

# Local caches / build outputs (reduce noise)
**/node_modules/**
**/.next/**
**/dist/**
**/build/**
**/.cache/**
**/__pycache__/**
**/.venv/**
**/.pytest_cache/**
